 Korn 的 Brian 'Head' Welch 分享了乐队新音乐的最新动态https://www.nme.com/news/music/korns-brian-head-welch-shares-update-on-new-music-from-the-band-3821020?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=korns-brian- Head-welch-分享乐队新音乐的更新Laura MolloyTue, 10 Dec 2024 21:44:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3821020 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不知道要多久——也许明年夏天，也许明年，下一个冬天，我不知道，但不会很快”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korns-brian-head-welch-shares-update-on-new-music-from-the-band-3821020">Korn 的 Brian &#39;Head&#39; Welch 分享了乐队新音乐的最新动态，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Brian-Head-Welch-of-Korn.-CREDIT_-Miikka-Skaffari_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/korn">Korn</a>的 Brian &#39;Head&#39; Welch 分享了他们下一张唱片的最新消息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/korn-requiem-nu-metal-start-the-healing-3155810">科恩：“在这张专辑中，我们的情感成长了。音乐可以治愈我们所有人”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支美国新金属乐队的上一张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/korn-requiem-review-3153065">Requiem</a> 》于 2022 年 2 月发行，从那时起他们就一直在酝酿推出后续专辑。</p><p>韦尔奇此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korns-brian-head-welch-says-therell-be-new-music-coming-next-year-3499301">表示，2024 年将会推出新音乐</a>，他告诉<a href="https://loudwire.com/brian-head-welch-new-korn-music-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Loudwire</em></a> ：“是的，明年会推出新音乐。我不知道，我们现在只是躲起来，做我们自己的事。”</p><p>但现在，他确认他们不会在年底前发布任何内容。韦尔奇在播客<em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I6-WQIDdXNk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Everblack</a></em>中谈到了他们目前的歌曲创作过程。 “是的，我们[写了很多]。我们仍在工作，”他说。</p><p>他接着说：“伙计，这是一次 30 年后的旅行，伙计，尝试继续这样做。我们对所得到的感到非常满意，但这需要一段时间。我不知道要多久——也许明年夏天，也许明年，下一个冬天，我不知道，但不会很快。” </p><figure id="attachment_3611818" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3611818" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3611818" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023.jpg" alt="KoRn 的布莱恩·韦尔奇 (Brian Welch)、乔纳森·戴维斯 (Jonathan Davis) 和詹姆斯·谢弗 (James Shaffer)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/korn-adidas-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3611818" class="wp-caption-text"> (LR) Brian Welch、Jonathan Davis 和 KoRn 的 James Shaffer 出席 2023 年 10 月 26 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶举行的 adidas Originals x KoRn 零售激活+媒体活动（图片来源：Phillip Faraone/Getty Images for adidas Originals）</figcaption></figure><p>去年，乐队分享了他们 2007 年专辑的豪华版，当时他们发行的专辑没有标题。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/korn-requiem-review-3153065"><i>NME</i>在对《安魂曲》的四星评论中表示</a>：“2019 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/korn-the-nothing-review-2544786">The Nothing</a> 》发现主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jonathan-davis">乔纳森·戴维斯 (Jonathan Davis)</a>被悲伤压垮了。后续专辑为乐队的唱片增添了一丝希望，”并补充道，“这将推动科恩的第一张‘快乐’专辑。更准确地说，《安魂曲》为唱片带来了一些新的东西，迄今为止，唱片一直是对人类苦难的探索。这导致了乐队迄今为止最细致入微的唱片。”</p><p>在其他地方，在他们最近的巡演中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-korn-play-deep-cut-hey-daddy-for-the-first-time-in-25-years-on-north-american-tour-3794067">Korn 25 年来首次现场演奏了深切的《Hey Daddy》</a> 。</p><p>不久之后，他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">伊凡塞斯乐队</a>的艾米·李一起合作演绎了《Freak On A Leash》。该表演是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-announce-30th-anniversary-stadium-show-with-evanescence-gojira-scars-on-broadway-and-more-3597555">洛杉矶特别演出</a>的一部分，旨在庆祝他们 1994 年首张同名专辑发行 30 周年。除了伊凡塞斯之外，作为特邀嘉宾的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">哥吉拉 (Gojira)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scars-on-broadway-1334362">百老汇疤痕 (Scars On Broadway)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a>等。</p><p>至于 2025 年的现场计划，Korn 将于明年夏天参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-2025-announced-stacked-line-up-with-green-day-sleep-token-korn-and-more-tickets-3812026">Download Festival</a>和法国的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-korn-muse-scorpions-turnstile-knocked-loose-lead-massive-hellfest-2025-line-up-3821000">HellFest</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korns-brian-head-welch-shares-update-on-new-music-from-the-band-3821020">Korn 的 Brian &#39;Head&#39; Welch 分享了乐队新音乐的最新动态，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
该死的老鼠疥疮出现在 Netflix 的新间谍剧《黑鸽子》中https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-damned-rat-scabies-appears-netflix-black-doves-3821006?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-damned-rat-scabies-appears-netflix-黑鸽子Max PilleyTue, 10 Dec 2024 21:32:57 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflixPunk https://www.nme.com/?p=3821006 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位传奇朋克鼓手与凯拉·奈特莉、本·卫肖和莎拉·兰开夏一起主演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-damned-rat-scabies-appears-netflix-black-doves-3821006">《该死的老鼠疥疮》出现在 Netflix 新间谍剧《黑鸽子》中的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/rat_scabies_damned-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix 的</a>新间谍惊悚片<i>《黑鸽子》</i>中出现了一位不太可能来自音乐界的客串明星： <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-damned">《The Damned</a> 》的鼓手 Rat Scabies。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="759" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/every-song-black-doves-soundtrack-netflix-3818929"><b>这是“黑鸽子”原声带中的每首歌</b></a></li></ul><p>在剧中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiera-knightly">凯拉·奈特莉</a>饰演英国国防部长的妻子，当她的爱人在涉及伦敦黑社会的事件中被杀时，她得知自己作为间谍的秘密身份正处于危险之中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ben-whishaw">本·威肖</a>饰演的角色被派去保护她。</p><p>莎拉·兰开夏尔 (Sarah Lancashire) 也在这部六集节目中担任主演，该节目现已在该平台上直播，但乐迷们也可以为传奇朋克人物 Scabies 的出现而感到高兴。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="黑鸽子|官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1R0d2jW7a-I?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>从第一集中，鼓手扮演宾果（Bingo），一家音乐商店的老板，可能与犯罪集团有秘密联系。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kiera-knightly-new-netflix-spy-thriller-black-doves-has-near-perfect-score-from-critics-3819724"><i>《黑鸽子》</i>获得了来自各方的好评</a>，目前在评论聚合网站<i>烂番茄</i>上的评分高达 98%。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="760" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-the-damneds-captain-sensible-3436110"><b>摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——《该死的明智队长》</b></a></li></ul><p> Rat Scabies 最近重新加入英国原创朋克界最具影响力的乐队之一 The Damned 后，迎来了重要的一年。与 David Vanian、Captain Sensible 和 Paul Gray 一起， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-damned-announce-2024-uk-tour-and-return-of-rat-scabies-buy-tickets-3545193">乐队目前正与该阵容一起进行超过 35 年的首次巡演</a>。</p><p>乐队将于周二（12 月 10 日）在伍尔弗汉普顿演出，剩余演出地点包括布里斯托尔、南安普顿、伊斯特本、剑桥，并于 12 月 18 日在伦敦 Roundhouse 演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/the-damned-tickets/artist/1606262?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=UM%3AWOmUSgxyPUN%3A1ovyuF3p-UkFXWTzhnRXHQA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>查找剩余门票。</p><p>继首张专辑《Damned Damned Damned》发行 47 年后，The Damned 还在今年早些时候发行了他们的第十二张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-damned-announce-new-album-darkadelic-share-new-single-the-invisible-man-3392122">Darkadelic</a> 》。</p><p>在其他地方，Captain Sensible 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-damned-on-how-lemmy-saved-the-band-3416931">谈到了他与 Motörhead 乐队成员 Lemmy Kilmister 的关系</a>，以及这位已故贝斯手如何“拯救”了乐队。 “如果没有莱米和他的鼓励，我认为我们不会继续下去，”他在接受采访时说道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-damned-rat-scabies-appears-netflix-black-doves-3821006">《该死的老鼠疥疮》出现在 Netflix 新间谍剧《黑鸽子》中的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
