zNPHI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>至于 Muse，该乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muses-chris-wolstenholme-launches-new-band-chromes-with-two-singles-imaginary-world-and-the-good-life-3803730">Chris Wolstenholme 上个月成为头条新闻，当时他推出了一支名为 Chromes 的新乐队</a>，并推出了两首新单曲。</p><p>在此之前，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-bellamy">马特·贝拉米</a>为<em>《1984》</em>的 Audible 版本录制了配乐，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-behind-the-scenes-video-of-muses-matt-bellamy-recording-new-1984-score-at-abbey-road-3613227">分享了整个过程的幕后花絮</a>。这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muse-matt-bellamy-scored-new-1984-audiobook-starring-andrew-garfield-3567775">根据乔治·奥威尔的反乌托邦经典小说改编的一部新的音频惊悚片</a>，该片于 4 月 4 日发布——距离主角写第一篇日记的日期正好 40 年。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-korn-muse-scorpions-turnstile-knocked-loose-lead-massive-hellfest-2025-line-up-3821000">Linkin Park、KoRn、Muse、Scorpions、Turnstile、Knocked Loose 领衔的 2025 年 HellFest 大型阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
英国配音和音响系统传奇人物 Ras Muffet 去世https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-dub-and-soundsystem-legend-ras-muffet-has-died-3821004?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=uk-dub-and-soundsystem-legend-拉斯·马菲特已死Anagricel DuranTue, 10 Dec 2024 20:39:46 +0000 Music NewsNews..Dub https://www.nme.com/?p=3821004 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位制作人和音响师以其经典曲目“Ethiopian King Dub”、“New Dawning”和“Play Fool Dubwise”而闻名</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-dub-and-soundsystem-legend-ras-muffet-has-died-3821004">英国后配音和音响系统传奇人物 Ras Muffet 去世，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>英国配音和音响系统传奇人物拉斯·穆菲特（Ras Muffet）——真名史蒂夫·约翰逊（Steve Johnson）——去世了。</p><p>他的品牌 Roots Injection 在与<a href="https://ra.co/news/81742" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Resident Advisor</em></a>分享的一份声明中证实了他的死亡消息。马菲特以其五十年来​​作为音响师和制作人的广泛工作而闻名，并创作了各种经典作品，如“Ethiopian King Dub”、“New Dawning”和“Trouble &amp; Strife”，其中一些成为音响系统的常规固定装置，例如Mighty Tabot、Channel One Sound、Aba Shanti-I 和 Iration Steppas。</p><p> Muffet 也是 Jah Shaka 的合伙人，也是 70 年代初传奇的 Jah Shaka 音响系统的成员。在 90 年代，Muffet 继续经营自己的厂牌——Roots Injection——该厂牌在连接配音和根雷鬼声音方面发挥了重要作用。 Roots Injection 积极参与双盘文化，并制作了专为音响系统冲突或特殊会议而创作的独家未发行曲目。</p><p>世界各地的 DJ、制作人、粉丝和音响团体都在社交媒体上向这位传奇人物致敬。</p><p> Jah Shaka 的家人在 Instagram 上分享了一篇纪念已故穆菲特的帖子，并配文写道：“我们谨向不幸去世的著名音乐制作人拉斯·穆菲特的家人和密友表示哀悼。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDATLHEicvf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://w