 “拯救铅磨坊的战斗已经到来”，标志性的谢菲尔德场馆走向法庭https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-fight-to-save-the-leadmill-is-here-as-iconic-sheffield-venue-heads-to-court-3820977?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=拯救铅厂的斗争在这里作为标志性的谢菲尔德场地前往法庭Laura MolloyTue, 10 Dec 2024 19:48:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3820977 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 是 Def Leppard 表演“One Night Only”的地方。图片日期：2023 年 5 月 19 日星期五。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自业主于 2022 年发出驱逐通知以来，该场馆的未来一直充满不确定性</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-fight-to-save-the-leadmill-is-here-as-iconic-sheffield-venue-heads-to-court-3820977">当标志性的谢菲尔德球场走向法庭时，“拯救 The Leadmill 的战斗已经到来”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 是 Def Leppard 表演“One Night Only”的地方。图片日期：2023 年 5 月 19 日星期五。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>下周将举行一场听证会，以确定谢菲尔德标志性音乐场所 The Leadmill 的未来。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/sheffield-leadmill-arctic-monkeys-closes-we-all-lose-something-3196736">如果谢菲尔德的 Leadmill——帮助击败北极猴子的场地——消失了，我们都会失去一些东西</a></strong></li></ul><p>自 2022 年以来，该场地一直受到威胁，此前该建筑的业主<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">发布了驱逐通知</a>，引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">整个音乐行业和演出观众的强烈抗议</a>。</p><p>该物业由多米尼克·马登 (Dominic Madden) 和雅各布·刘易斯 (Jacob Lewis) 的合资企业 Electric Group 所有，该集团还拥有伦敦的 Electric Brixton、布里斯托尔的 SWX 和纽卡斯尔的 NX。他们于 2017 年购买了该场地的永久业权，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffield-leadmill-bosses-claim-landlords-are-exterminating-them-after-they-denied-plans-to-close-venue-3195917">曾表示，在终止当前占用者的租约时，他们无意关闭该场地</a>。</p><p>然而，管理层很快反击， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffield-leadmill-bosses-claim-landlords-are-exterminating-them-after-they-denied-plans-to-close-venue-3195917">称他们正在“被房东消灭”，</a>然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-calls-on-fans-to-object-to-landlords-premises-licence-application-3444836">又向粉丝发出新的呼吁，在透露房东正在推进驱逐计划后寻求支持</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-owners-of-sheffields-the-leadmill-respond-to-venues-anti-eviction-campaign-3445232">马登随后再次回应</a>，加倍声称他们“打算继续将该空间作为音乐场所运营，专注于演出、俱乐部之夜和喜剧活动的多样化组合。”</p><p>五月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-wins-first-court-battle-to-avoid-eviction-from-landlord-3758561">The Leadmill 在更换其法律团队并提出各种意见书来解释为什么他们认为房东的做法不合法后，赢得了与房东的第一场官司</a>。</p><p>该场馆的法律团队当时获准休会，以便他们准备新的论点并对电气集团提交的证据做出回应。 </p><figure id="attachment_3758583" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3758583" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3758583" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰米·韦伯斯特 (Jamie Webster) 在谢菲尔德 The Leadmill 的舞台上现场表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Jamie-Webster@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3758583" class="wp-caption-text">杰米·韦伯斯特 (Jamie Webster) 在谢菲尔德 The Leadmill 的舞台上现场表演。 （Robin Burns/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，下一阶段的法律诉讼即将到来，定于 12 月 16 日、18 日和 20 日在利兹财产和商业法院进行。</p><p>昨天（12 月 9 日），场地代表在 Instagram 上写道，“拯救 The Leadmill 的战斗已经到来”，并补充道：“近 45 年来，The Leadmill 一直是谢菲尔德音乐、艺术和文化场景的基石，为新兴艺术家提供平台，为我们的社区提供难忘的夜晚。</p><p> “现在，我们正在努力阻止房东根据第 25 条 G 地的规定驱逐我们，这一举动不仅威胁到我们的场地，还威胁到谢菲尔德文化身份的核心以及数百万其他企业。”</p><p>他们接着说：“这不仅仅是一栋建筑的问题，而是维护文化空间的价值以及保护英国各地独立场馆和企业的重要性。强迫我们走上街头不仅会破坏和削弱更广泛的社区，而且所有 Leadmill 员工都将在房东手中失去工作和生计。</p><p> “如果我们输掉这场战斗，每个商业租户都将面临风险。这将为文化机构和企业树立一个危险的先例。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系 Electric Group 发言人征求意见。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDXeyMSP9Fy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 C561.058,72.155 560.06,72.803 558.662,73.347 C557.607,73.757 556.021,74.244 553.102,74.378 C549.944,74.521 548.997,74.552 541,74.552 C533.003,74.552 532.056,74.521 528.898,74.378 C525.979,74.244 524.393,73.757 523.338,73.347 C521.94,72.803 520.942,72.155 519.894,71.106 C518.846,70.057 518.